data.description: Welcome home! This all brick, corner lot home is located minutes from i25 and all of the amenities that Thornton has to offer. The curb appeal is welcoming with mature trees, in a quiet, peaceful neighborhood. Upon entry you are greeted with a dedicated entry that opens up to the living room and kitchen. The open floor plan is inviting, bright and clean. This home has updated kitchen, bathrooms and newer floors throughout. This ranch has all rooms on one level, a plus for ease of movement throughout the entire home. The oversized laundry room has a utility sink and room for storage, or even a sunroom. The backyard has an insulated shed and access to the 2 car, detached garage. There is also a brick paved space for a 3rd car to park. The covered patio offers relief from the hot Colorado sun in the summers.  This is the perfect home with schools and parks minutes away. Don't miss your chance to purchase a home under 450K in the awesome town of Thornton!
